==疾病和死亡==
比爾·派斯頓13歲時因為[[風溼熱|風溼熱]]導致心臟瓣膜受損<ref>{{cite web|url=http://extratv.com/2017/03/02/bill-paxtons-secret-health-battle-what-was-wrong-with-his-heart/|title=Bill Paxton's Secret Health Battle — What Was Wrong with His Heart?|access-date=2021-07-13|archive-date=2021-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210717055109/https://extratv.com/2017/03/02/bill-paxtons-secret-health-battle-what-was-wrong-with-his-heart/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在2017年2月14日接受[[心脏外科|開胸手術]]，修補受損心瓣和[[主動脈|主動脈]]<ref>[https://deadline.com/2017/03/bill-paxton-dies-obituary-twister-big-love-1201999634/ Bill Paxton Died Of Stroke Following Surgery – Update] {{Wayback|url=https://deadline.com/2017/03/bill-paxton-dies-obituary-twister-big-love-1201999634/ |date=20210716112709 }} March 6, 2017.</ref><ref name=strickland>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnn.com/2017/03/06/health/bill-paxton-death-stroke/index.html|work=CNN|title=Bill Paxton's death caused by stroke after surgery|author=Strickland, Ashley|date=March 7, 2017|access-date=January 28, 2018|archive-date=2021-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210716112522/https://www.cnn.com/2017/03/06/health/bill-paxton-death-stroke/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。手術後11天，比爾·派斯頓[[中風|中風]]逝世，享年61歲<ref name="NBC News">{{cite web|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/actor-bill-paxton-dead-61-due-complications-surgery-n725776|title=Actor Bill Paxton Dead at 61 Due to Complications from Surgery|access-date=February 26, 2017|archive-date=2019-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190430034250/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/actor-bill-paxton-dead-61-due-complications-surgery-n725776|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2017/feb/27/bill-paxton-obituary|title=Bill Paxton obituary|first=Ryan|last=Gilbey|date=February 27, 2017|newspaper=The Guardian|accessdate=2021-07-13|archive-date=2021-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211206150519/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2017/feb/27/bill-paxton-obituary|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|work=The Mercury News|url=https://www.mercurynews.com/2017/03/07/bill-paxtons-death-related-to-heart-disease-childhood-illness/|title=Bill Paxton's death related to heart defect and possibly to childhood illness|author=Ross, Martha|date=March 7, 2017|access-date=January 27, 2018|archive-date=2021-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210713100900/https://www.mercurynews.com/2017/03/07/bill-paxtons-death-related-to-heart-disease-childhood-illness/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他死後遺體被[[火化|火化]]並安葬於{{le|森林草坪紀念公園 (好萊塢山)|Forest Lawn Memorial Park (Hollywood Hills)|森林草坪紀念公園}}（Forest Lawn Memorial Park of Hollywood Hills）<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.wbaltv.com/article/cause-of-death-revealed-for-bill-paxton/9097231 |title=Cause of death revealed for Bill Paxton |date=March 6, 2017 |work=WBAL |access-date=June 1, 2018 |language=en |archive-date=2021-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210716112532/https://www.wbaltv.com/article/cause-of-death-revealed-for-bill-paxton/9097231 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

